message.reasoning_content:
Hmm, user wants a single-sentence prompt under 40 words for an autonomous delivery fleet optimization task. Need to include live data analysis, parameter adjustments within safety limits, results monitoring, and performance reporting.

The prompt must be concise yet cover all specified elements. Can combine "analyze live traffic and battery data" to save words. "Adjust routing and charging parameters" captures the tunable aspects. "Monitor outcomes and report efficiency gains" wraps up the monitoring and reporting components.

Keeping it under 40 words means avoiding connectors like "while" or "and then." Just state the core actions sequentially. The current draft fits at 18 words.
